== 美容外科處置 ==
美容外科是對身體正常部位進行的自願性或選擇性手術，其唯一目的是改善人的外表或消除[[老化|老化]]跡象。2014年僅在美國就進行了近1600萬例美容處置<ref>{{cite web|title=Archived copy|url=http://www.plasticsurgery.org/Documents/news-resources/statistics/2014-statistics/plastic-surgery-statsitics-full-report.pdf|accessdate=2016-03-31|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402095506/http://www.plasticsurgery.org/Documents/news-resources/statistics/2014-statistics/plastic-surgery-statsitics-full-report.pdf|archivedate=2 April 2016|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。自21世紀初以來在美國進行的美容處置數量增加幾乎一倍，2014年接受美容處置者有92％是女性，高於2001年的88％<ref>{{cite web|title=2001 Cosmetic Surgery Statistics|url=http://www.cosmeticplasticsurgerystatistics.com/statistics-2001.html|accessdate=12 September 2015|publisher=|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304095918/http://www.cosmeticplasticsurgerystatistics.com/statistics-2001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年進行了近1200萬例美容處置，其中前五個最常見的手術是[[隆胸|隆胸]]、[[抽脂|抽脂]]、[[縮胸|縮胸]]、[[眼瞼|眼瞼]]手術、{{Le|腹部整形|Abdominoplasty}}。{{Le|美國美容外科醫學會|American Society for Aesthetic Plastic Surgery}}調查了34種美容處置的統計數據，其中19種處置是外科手術，例如鼻外觀整型手術或{{Le|拉皮手術|Rhytidectomy}}；非手術處置包括注射[[肉毒桿菌毒素|肉毒桿菌毒素]]和{{Le|雷射除毛|Laser hair removal}}。2010年的調查顯示美國總計有9336814例處置，其中1622290例是外科手術，同時也發現接受處置者絕大多數（81％）為[[高加索人種|高加索人種]]（白人）<ref>{{cite journal|title=Cosmetic Surgery National Data Bank Statistics|author=Society for Aesthetic Plastic Surgery|date=2010|journal=Aesthetic Surgery Journal|pages=1–18}}</ref>。

{{le|美國整形外科醫學會|American Society of Plastic Surgeons}}估計2005年美國18歲以下有超過333000例接受美容處置，1996年僅約14000例，這些統計數字有其意義，鼓勵年輕人在未來繼續接受這些美容處置<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Teenagers and cosmetic surgery: focus on breast augmentation and liposuction|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18809128|last=Zuckerman|first=Diana|last2=Abraham|first2=Anisha|date=2008-10|journal=The Journal of Adolescent Health: Official Publication of the Society for Adolescent Medicine|issue=4|doi=10.1016/j.jadohealth.2008.04.018|volume=43|pages=318–324|issn=1879-1972|pmid=18809128|access-date=2021-10-26|archive-date=2021-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211026142148/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18809128/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在美國利用{{le|種族整形外科|Ethnic plastic surgery}}的美容處置跨越種族界限的人逐漸增加，非洲裔、亞裔、西班牙裔和[[美國白人|美國白人]]皆然。在[[英國|英國]]的1191篇報紙文章中，其中89％使用「整形手術」一詞討論到美容手術，有意義的顯示了西方世界描述美容手術的頻率<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Plastic surgery in the press|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18675242|last=Reid|first=A. J.|last2=Malone|first2=P. S. C.|date=2008-08|journal=Journal of plastic, reconstructive & aesthetic surgery: JPRAS|issue=8|doi=10.1016/j.bjps.2008.06.012|volume=61|pages=866–869|issn=1878-0539|pmid=18675242|access-date=2021-10-26|archive-date=2021-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211027205902/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18675242/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[亞洲|亞洲]]，美容手術變得越來越流行，[[中國|中國]]和[[印度|印度]]等國家已經成為亞洲最大的美容手術市場<ref>{{Cite web|title=India, China Among Plastic Surgery Capitals|url=https://www.webmd.com/beauty/news/20100809/india-china-among-plastic-surgery-capitals|access-date=2021-10-26|last=Mann|first=Denise|work=WebMD|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211027224022/https://www.webmd.com/beauty/news/20100809/india-china-among-plastic-surgery-capitals|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[大韩民国|南韓]]因為專業於顏面骨骼的手術，也越來越流行美容手術，南韓外科醫師團隊關於顏面骨骼輪廓手術的第一篇發表文章圖解說明該類手術的多種方法<ref name=":0">{{Cite book|title=Facial bone contouring surgery: a practical guide|date=2017|publisher=Springer|last=Park|first=Sanghoon|isbn=9789811027260|location=Singapore|oclc=1004601615}}</ref>。

== 併發症與風險 ==
所有手術都有風險。美容外科常見的[[併發症|併發症]]包括[[血腫|血腫]]、{{le|神經損傷|Nerve injury}}、[[感染|感染]]、[[疤痕|疤痕]]增生、{{le|植入物故障|Implant failure}}、[[器官|器官]]損傷<ref>{{Cite web|title=10 Common Plastic Surgery Complications: Hematoma, Infection, More|url=https://www.healthline.com/health/most-common-plastic-surgery-complications|access-date=2021-10-26|date=2015-02-04|work=Healthline|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211026142201/https://www.healthline.com/health/most-common-plastic-surgery-complications|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Plastic surgery – Complications – NHS Choices|url=http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/Plastic-surgery/Pages/Complications.aspx|accessdate=2020-04-15|date=23 October 2017|last=Choices|first=NHS|website=www.nhs.uk|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003194216/http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/Plastic-surgery/Pages/Complications.aspx|archive-date=2017-10-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Cosmetic surgery Risks – Mayo Clinic|url=http://www.mayoclinic.org/tests-procedures/cosmetic-surgery/basics/risks/prc-20022389|accessdate=2020-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702083741/http://www.mayoclinic.org/tests-procedures/cosmetic-surgery/basics/risks/prc-20022389|archive-date=2017-07-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[乳房|乳房]]植入物可有許多併發症，包括破裂。2011年[[美國食品藥品監督管理局|美國食品藥品監督管理局]]表示：有五分之一接受[[隆胸|隆胸]]的病患在植入後10年內必須將其移除<ref>{{Cite web|title=FDA provides updated safety data on silicone gel-filled breast implants|url=https://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm260235.htm|accessdate=2020-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111103032451/https://www.fda.gov/NewsEvents/Newsroom/PressAnnouncements/ucm260235.htm|archive-date=2011-11-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 精神疾患 ==
儘管[[媒體|媒體]]和[[廣告|廣告]]扮演著重要的角色並影響許多人的生活，比如讓人們相信美容手術是一個可行的方式，能改變自己讓人更喜歡<ref>{{Cite journal|title=‘I Want to Look Like That!’: Cosmetic Surgery and Celebrity Culture|url=http://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/1749975510391583|last=Elliott|first=Anthony|date=2011-12|journal=Cultural Sociology|issue=4|doi=10.1177/1749975510391583|volume=5|pages=463–477|language=en|issn=1749-9755|access-date=2021-10-26|archive-date=2021-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211028094611/https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/1749975510391583|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但研究人員認為某些人對美容手術的著迷與[[精神疾患|精神疾患]]有關，比如[[體象障礙|體象障礙]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Prevalence of Body Dysmorphic Disorder in Plastic Surgery and Dermatology Patients: A Systematic Review with Meta-Analysis|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28411353|last=Ribeiro|first=Rafael Vilela Eiras|date=2017-08|journal=Aesthetic Plastic Surgery|issue=4|doi=10.1007/s00266-017-0869-0|volume=41|pages=964–970|issn=1432-5241|pmid=28411353|access-date=2021-10-26|archive-date=2021-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211028094610/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28411353/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，病患偏愛接受美容整形手術以矯正自己臆想的外觀缺陷，這樣的行為與體象障礙具有相關性<ref name="PMJBDD">{{Cite journal|title=Body dysmorphic disorder|url=https://pmj.bmj.com/lookup/doi/10.1136/pmj.2003.015289|last=Veale|first=D|date=2004-02-01|journal=Postgraduate Medical Journal|issue=940|doi=10.1136/pmj.2003.015289|volume=80|pages=67–71|language=en|issn=0032-5473|pmc=PMC1742928|pmid=14970291}}</ref>。

在某些情況下，醫生拒絕進一步再做任何整形手術，病患可能轉作{{le|自我手術|Self-surgery}}，自己注射藥劑，帶來極大的安全風險<ref>{{Cite news|last=Canning|first=Andrea|title=Woman's DIY Plastic Surgery 'Nightmare'|newspaper=ABC News|date=20 July 2009|url=http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/story?id=8080723&page=1|accessdate=2020-04-15|archive-date=2018-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180409023206/http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/story?id=8080723&page=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

